{"id":603,"parent_id":497,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":603,"title":"Psalm 106","subtitle":"","short_title":"Ps.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/106","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Psalm 106"],[".studySummary",["i","Praise the Lord for His mercy and mighty works—Israel rebelled and did wickedly—Moses mediated between Israel and the Lord—Israel was scattered and slain for worshipping false gods."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/106.1","order":"02.20.106.39428"},["b","1"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"Praise ye the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"]],". O give thanks unto the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"; for",["i","he is"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"good"],": for his mercy",["i","endureth"],"for ever."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/106.2","order":"02.20.106.39429"},["b","2"],"Who can utter the mighty",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"acts"],"of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"?",["i","who"],"can shew forth all his praise?"],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/106.3","order":"02.20.106.39430"},["b","3"],"Blessed",["i","are"],"they that keep judgment,",["i","and"],"he that doeth righteousness at all times."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/106.4","order":"02.20.106.39431"},["b","4"],"Remember me, O",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", with the favour",["i","that thou bearest unto"],"thy people: O visit me with thy salvation;"],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/106.5","order":"02.20.106.39432"},["b","5"],"That I may see the good of thy chosen, that I may rejoice in the gladness of thy nation, that I may glory with thine inheritance."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/106.6","order":"02.20.106.39433"},["b","6"],"We have",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"sinned"],"with our fathers, we have committed iniquity, we have done wickedly."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/106.7","order":"02.20.106.39434"},["b","7"],"Our fathers understood not thy wonders in Egypt; they remembered not the multitude of thy mercies; but",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"provoked"],["i","him"],"at the sea,",["i","even"],"at the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_7b"},"Red sea"],"."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/106.8","order":"02.20.106.39435"},["b","8"],"Nevertheless he saved them for his",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"name’s"],"sake, that he might make his mighty",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_8b"},"power"],"to be known."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/106.9","order":"02.20.106.39436"},["b","9"],"He",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"rebuked"],"the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_9b"},"Red sea"],"also, and it was dried up: so he led them through the depths, as through the wilderness."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/106.10","order":"02.20.106.39437"},["b","10"],"And he saved them from the hand of him that hated",["i","them,"],"and redeemed them from the hand of the enemy."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/106.11","order":"02.20.106.39438"},["b","11"],"And the waters covered their enemies: there was not",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"one"],"of them left."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/106.12","order":"02.20.106.39439"},["b","12"],"Then believed they his words; they sang his praise."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/106.13","order":"02.20.106.39440"},["b","13"],"They soon forgat his works; they waited not for his counsel:"],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/106.14","order":"02.20.106.39441"},["b","14"],"But",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"lusted"],"exceedingly in the wilderness, and tempted God in the desert."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/106.15","order":"02.20.106.39442"},["b","15"],"And he gave them their request; but sent leanness into their soul."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/106.16","order":"02.20.106.39443"},["b","16"],"They",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"envied"],"Moses also in the camp,",["i","and"],"Aaron the saint of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/106.17","order":"02.20.106.39444"},["b","17"],"The earth",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"opened"],"and swallowed up Dathan, and covered the company of Abiram."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/106.18","order":"02.20.106.39445"},["b","18"],"And a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"fire"],"was kindled in their company; the flame burned up the wicked."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/106.19","order":"02.20.106.39446"},["b","19"],"They made a calf in Horeb, and worshipped the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"molten image"],"."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/106.20","order":"02.20.106.39447"},["b","20"],"Thus they changed their glory into the similitude of an ox that eateth grass."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/106.21","order":"02.20.106.39448"},["b","21"],"They forgat God their saviour, which had done great things in Egypt;"],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/106.22","order":"02.20.106.39449"},["b","22"],"Wondrous works in the land of Ham,",["i","and"],"terrible things by the Red sea."],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/106.23","order":"02.20.106.39450"},["b","23"],"Therefore he said that he would",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_23a"},"destroy"],"them, had not Moses his chosen stood before him in the breach, to turn away his wrath, lest he should destroy",["i","them."]],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/106.24","order":"02.20.106.39451"},["b","24"],"Yea, they despised the pleasant land, they",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_24a"},"believed not"],"his word:"],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/106.25","order":"02.20.106.39452"},["b","25"],"But",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_25a"},"murmured"],"in their tents,",["i","and"],"hearkened not unto the voice of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"26","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/106.26","order":"02.20.106.39453"},["b","26"],"Therefore he lifted up his hand against them, to overthrow them in the wilderness:"],["div",{"id":"27","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/106.27","order":"02.20.106.39454"},["b","27"],"To overthrow their seed also among the nations, and to scatter them in the lands."],["div",{"id":"28","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/106.28","order":"02.20.106.39455"},["b","28"],"They joined themselves also unto",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_28a"},"Baal-peor"],", and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_28b"},"ate"],"the sacrifices",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_28c"},"of"],"the dead."],["div",{"id":"29","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/106.29","order":"02.20.106.39456"},["b","29"],"Thus they provoked",["i","him"],"to anger with their",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_29a"},"inventions"],": and the plague brake in upon them."],["div",{"id":"30","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/106.30","order":"02.20.106.39457"},["b","30"],"Then stood up",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_30a"},"Phinehas"],", and executed judgment: and",["i","so"],"the plague was stayed."],["div",{"id":"31","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/106.31","order":"02.20.106.39458"},["b","31"],"And that was counted unto him for righteousness unto all generations for evermore."],["div",{"id":"32","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/106.32","order":"02.20.106.39459"},["b","32"],"They angered",["i","him"],"also at the waters of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_32a"},"strife"],", so that it went ill with Moses for their",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_32b"},"sakes"],":"],["div",{"id":"33","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/106.33","order":"02.20.106.39460"},["b","33"],"Because they provoked his spirit, so that he",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_33a"},"spake"],"unadvisedly with his lips."],["div",{"id":"34","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/106.34","order":"02.20.106.39461"},["b","34"],"They did not",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_34a"},"destroy"],"the nations, concerning whom the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"commanded them:"],["div",{"id":"35","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/106.35","order":"02.20.106.39462"},["b","35"],"But were",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_35a"},"mingled"],"among the heathen, and learned their works."],["div",{"id":"36","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/106.36","order":"02.20.106.39463"},["b","36"],"And they served their",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_36a"},"idols"],": which were a snare unto them."],["div",{"id":"37","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/106.37","order":"02.20.106.39464"},["b","37"],"Yea, they sacrificed their sons and their daughters unto devils,"],["div",{"id":"38","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/106.38","order":"02.20.106.39465"},["b","38"],"And shed innocent",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_38a"},"blood"],",",["i","even"],"the blood of their sons and of their daughters, whom they sacrificed unto the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_38b"},"idols"],"of Canaan: and the land was polluted with blood."],["div",{"id":"39","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/106.39","order":"02.20.106.39466"},["b","39"],"Thus were they defiled with their own works, and went a whoring with their own inventions."],["div",{"id":"40","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/106.40","order":"02.20.106.39467"},["b","40"],"Therefore was the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_40a"},"wrath"],"of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"kindled against his people, insomuch that he abhorred his own inheritance."],["div",{"id":"41","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/106.41","order":"02.20.106.39468"},["b","41"],"And he gave them into the hand of the heathen; and they that hated them ruled over them."],["div",{"id":"42","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/106.42","order":"02.20.106.39469"},["b","42"],"Their",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_42a"},"enemies"],"also",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_42b"},"oppressed"],"them, and they were brought into subjection under their hand."],["div",{"id":"43","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/106.43","order":"02.20.106.39470"},["b","43"],"Many times did he deliver them; but they provoked",["i","him"],"with their counsel, and were brought low for their iniquity."],["div",{"id":"44","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/106.44","order":"02.20.106.39471"},["b","44"],"Nevertheless he regarded their affliction, when he heard their cry:"],["div",{"id":"45","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/106.45","order":"02.20.106.39472"},["b","45"],"And he remembered for them his",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_45a"},"covenant"],", and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_45b"},"repented"],"according to the multitude of his mercies."],["div",{"id":"46","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/106.46","order":"02.20.106.39473"},["b","46"],"He made them also to be pitied of all those that carried them captives."],["div",{"id":"47","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/106.47","order":"02.20.106.39474"},["b","47"],"Save us, O",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"our God, and gather us from among the heathen, to give thanks unto thy holy name,",["i","and"],"to triumph in thy praise."],["div",{"id":"48","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/106.48","order":"02.20.106.39475"},["b","48"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_48a"},"Blessed"],["i","be"],"the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"God of Israel from everlasting to everlasting: and let all the people say, Amen. Praise ye the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/106.1a","order":"02.20.106.39476"},["b","1a"],["span.small","HEB"],["span.translit",["span.emphasis","Hallelu-yah"]],"(Hallelujah)."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/106.1b","order":"02.20.106.39478"},["b","1b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/119.68"},"Ps. 119:68"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/106.2a","order":"02.20.106.39480"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/4.8"},"Jacob 4:8"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/106.6a","order":"02.20.106.39482"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/14.20"},"Jer. 14:20"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/dan/9.5.5-6"},"Dan. 9:5 (5–6)"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/106.7a","order":"02.20.106.39484"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/14.11.11-12"},"Ex. 14:11 (11–12)"],"."],["div",{"id":"7b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/106.7b","order":"02.20.106.39486"},["b","7b"],["span.small","HEB"],"Reed Sea."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/106.8a","order":"02.20.106.39488"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/9.16"},"Ex. 9:16"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/63.14"},"Isa. 63:14"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/20.9"},"Ezek. 20:9"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/36.22"},"36:22"],"."],["div",{"id":"8b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/106.8b","order":"02.20.106.39490"},["b","8b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/18.1"},"Ex. 18:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/106.9a","order":"02.20.106.39492"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/7.2"},"2 Ne. 7:2"],"."],["div",{"id":"9b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/106.9b","order":"02.20.106.39494"},["b","9b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/14.21.1-31"},"Ex. 14:21 (1–31)"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/106.11a","order":"02.20.106.39496"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/14.28"},"Ex. 14:28"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/106.14a","order":"02.20.106.39498"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/lust"},"TG Lust"],"."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/106.16a","order":"02.20.106.39500"},["b","16a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/envy"},"TG Envy"],"."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/106.17a","order":"02.20.106.39502"},["b","17a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/num/16.32.30-35"},"Num. 16:32 (30–35)"],"."],["div",{"id":"18a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/106.18a","order":"02.20.106.39504"},["b","18a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/num/16.35"},"Num. 16:35"],"."],["div",{"id":"19a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/106.19a","order":"02.20.106.39506"},["b","19a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/32.4"},"Ex. 32:4"],"."],["div",{"id":"23a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/106.23a","order":"02.20.106.39508"},["b","23a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/32.10.10-11,32"},"Ex. 32:10 (10–11, 32)"],"."],["div",{"id":"24a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/106.24a","order":"02.20.106.39510"},["b","24a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/unbelief"},"TG Unbelief"],"."],["div",{"id":"25a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/106.25a","order":"02.20.106.39512"},["b","25a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/murmuring"},"TG Murmuring"],"."],["div",{"id":"28a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/106.28a","order":"02.20.106.39514"},["b","28a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/9.10"},"Hosea 9:10"],"."],["div",{"id":"28b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/106.28b","order":"02.20.106.39516"},["b","28b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/34.15"},"Ex. 34:15"],"."],["div",{"id":"28c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/106.28c","order":"02.20.106.39518"},["b","28c"],["span.small","IE"],"offered to."],["div",{"id":"29a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/106.29a","order":"02.20.106.39520"},["b","29a"],["span.small","HEB"],"doings."],["div",{"id":"30a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/106.30a","order":"02.20.106.39522"},["b","30a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/num/25.7.7-8"},"Num. 25:7 (7–8)"],"."],["div",{"id":"32a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/106.32a","order":"02.20.106.39524"},["b","32a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/47.19"},"Ezek. 47:19"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/strife"},"TG Strife"],"."],["div",{"id":"32b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/106.32b","order":"02.20.106.39526"},["b","32b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/1.37"},"Deut. 1:37"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/3.26"},"3:26"],"."],["div",{"id":"33a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/106.33a","order":"02.20.106.39528"},["b","33a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/num/20.10"},"Num. 20:10"],"."],["div",{"id":"34a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/106.34a","order":"02.20.106.39530"},["b","34a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/judg/1.21.21,27-36"},"Judg. 1:21 (21, 27–36)"],"."],["div",{"id":"35a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/106.35a","order":"02.20.106.39532"},["b","35a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/judg/3.5.5-6"},"Judg. 3:5 (5–6)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/2.6"},"Isa. 2:6"],"."],["div",{"id":"36a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/106.36a","order":"02.20.106.39534"},["b","36a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/apostasy-of-israel"},"TG Apostasy of Israel"],"."],["div",{"id":"38a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/106.38a","order":"02.20.106.39536"},["b","38a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/2.34.31-37"},"Jer. 2:34 (31–37)"],"."],["div",{"id":"38b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/106.38b","order":"02.20.106.39538"},["b","38b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/idolatry"},"TG Idolatry"],"."],["div",{"id":"40a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/106.40a","order":"02.20.106.39540"},["b","40a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/moses/7.34"},"Moses 7:34"],"."],["div",{"id":"42a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/106.42a","order":"02.20.106.39542"},["b","42a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lev/26.38"},"Lev. 26:38"],"."],["div",{"id":"42b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/106.42b","order":"02.20.106.39544"},["b","42b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/judg/4.3"},"Judg. 4:3"],"."],["div",{"id":"45a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/106.45a","order":"02.20.106.39546"},["b","45a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/74.20"},"Ps. 74:20"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/14.21"},"Jer. 14:21"],"."],["div",{"id":"45b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/106.45b","order":"02.20.106.39548"},["b","45b"],["span.small","HEB"],"relented.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/judg/2.18"},"Judg. 2:18"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/moses/8.25"},"Moses 8:25"],"."],["div",{"id":"48a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/106.48a","order":"02.20.106.39550"},["b","48a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/72.18"},"Ps. 72:18"],"."]]}
